step 1:
Create a VPC with 2 public subnets and 2 private subnets, and attach IGW/NAT and route tables.
10.0.0.0/16 -vpc
10.0.1.0/24 - subnets
10.0.2.0/24 - subnets
10.0.3.0/24 -subnets
10.0.4.0/24 - subnets

Step 2:
create a public instance and attach EIP to it
install basic apache2 page

Step 3:
Create a back-up image (AMI) for above created instance

Step 4:
create a new instance using backup and associate same EIP to this instance (remove EIP from first instance)
and check the page status 

Step 5: 
Create a windows public server and connect using RDP from your local laptop

